item.title: How Do I Make A Teleporting Emote Tab?
item.dc:creator: @The_Dark_Abbys The Dark Abbys
item.description:
@The_Dark_Abbys wrote:

Firstly you have to make a command to tele to that area, you do this by opening client.java

Search for if (command then find one of your teleportation commands, and copy and paste it

Adding in your new coords, i cbf going through it all

Now for emote tab find case 168:

And add under it

if(teleblock == true){ //Made by musicmad441 sendMessage("A magical force stops you from teleporting."); } else { customCommand("COMMANDYOUMADEEARLIER"); //made by Musicmad441 } break;

Good luck
—The Dark Abbys—
